title: Moto Racer 4 v1.5 + 3 DLC
description:
Release date: November 3, 2016
Genre: Artefacts Studio
Developer: Microids
Publisher:
Platform: PC
Engine: Unreal Engine 4
User ratings on Steam: 53% of user reviews - positive (26 reviews)

Included DLC :

Moto Racer 4 - Skewer
Moto Racer 4 - Space Dasher
Moto Racer 4 - The Truth

Moto Racer 4 is the continuation of the legendary series of motocross games, which took all the best from past games, and all this will be flavored with modern game engine Unreal Engine 4 and graphics. Players are not only motocross, but also races on powerful sports bikes on sports tracks and high-speed tracks.

The development was conducted under the guidance of the author of the original trilogy - Paul Cusset, and Artefacts Studio created 15 new game modes for single and multiplayer games, which will be supplemented by the already classic Time Trial, Single race and Championship modes.
